steps.instruction:
### Prep
- Slice the plum tomatoes

### Steps
1. Preheat oven to 400F
2. Spread potatoes evenly in 2-quart baking dish
3. lice tomatoes and halve cheese slices; arrange tomato and cheese slices, alternating and overlapping layers (shingle) over top of potatoes
4. Combine bread crumbs and Parmesan cheese; sprinkle over tomatoes
5. Bake 2025 minutes or until potatoes are hot and topping has browned
6. Serve
